## 4. PROJECT STRUCTURE

This is a small focused MVP. Structure must be clean but not over-engineered.
One Service per business concept. One Controller per resource. That is enough.

app/
├── Models/
│   ├── Product.php
│   ├── RawMaterial.php
│   ├── BillOfMaterial.php
│   ├── PurchaseRequest.php
│   └── RFQ.php
│
├── Http/
│   ├── Controllers/
│   │   ├── PurchaseRequestController.php
│   │   └── RFQController.php
│   │
│   └── Requests/
│       ├── StorePurchaseRequestRequest.php
│       └── StoreRFQRequest.php
│
└── Services/
    ├── PurchaseRequestService.php
    ├── RFQService.php
    └── PDFGeneratorService.php

resources/views/
├── layouts/
│   └── app.blade.php
├── purchase-requests/
│   ├── index.blade.php
│   ├── create.blade.php
│   └── show.blade.php
└── rfqs/
    ├── show.blade.php
    └── pdf.blade.php

database/
├── migrations/
└── seeders/
    └── DatabaseSeeder.php  ← seed products, materials, vendors for demo

routes/
└── web.php

